NBP OFFERS TO DRAIN PLN 250 MLN FOR 14 DAYS . The National Bank of Polandoffered to drain 250 million zlotys , in nominal terms , off themarket for 14 days through a reverse NBP - bill repurchaseauction , the bank said . Deadline hour - 12 : 00 Date of settlement - January 17 , 1997 Repurchase - January 31 , 1997 Discount rate ( pct ) - 20 . 00Maturity of bills offered - February 14 , 1997 - - Warsaw Newsroom + 48 22 653 9700 
